              "name": "email_text",
              "value": "=Got it, {{ $json.contact_first_name }}.\n\nWe received the {{ $json.document_label }} you uploaded for {{ $node['03 · Postgres · Fetch Context'].json.sub_name }} on behalf of {{ $node['03 · Postgres · Fetch Context'].json.gc_name_safe }}.\n\nIt's in compliance review now. We'll reach out if anything is missing.\n\nReceipt:\n  Document: {{ $json.document_label }}\n  Uploaded: {{ new Date($node['03 · Postgres · Fetch Context'].json.uploaded_at).toUTCString() }}\n  Reference: {{ $node['03 · Postgres · Fetch Context'].json.token }}\n\n— Blackflowcode.ai · hello@blackflowcodeai.com · 516.604.1804",
              "type": "string"
